  <section id="tips">
    <h2>Safety Tips for Everyone</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Always be aware of your surroundings:</strong> Pay attention to what's going on around you.</li>
      <li><strong>Trust your instincts:</strong> If something feels wrong, remove yourself from the situation.</li>
      <li><strong>Know emergency contacts:</strong> Make sure you have important numbers stored in your phone or on hand.</li>
      <li><strong>Stay connected:</strong> Let someone know where you are and who you're with, especially if you're going somewhere new.</li>
      <li><strong>Look out for each other:</strong> Be a good friend, and if someone is in danger, make sure to help or call for assistance.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

